Title: Improved VIV response prediction using adaptive parameters and data
  clustering
Authors: Jie Wu and Decao Yin and Halvor Lie and Signe Riemer-S{\o}rensen and
  Svein S{\ae}vik and Michael Triantafyllou
Categories: cs.CE
